dibabel-diff-content--login-error: Please login in the upper right corner before copying.
dibabel-diff-header-description--diverge: The current version of $1 was not found in the history of the primary page $2.
dibabel-diff-header-description--ok: Page $1 is a localized version of the original $2.
dibabel-diff-header-description--unlocal: Page $1 is identical with the original $2, but needs to have some localizations.
dibabel-diff-header-warnings--dependenci: The following dependencies are not present on the destination site. Copy these pages to $1 and make sure they are linked to other wikis.
dibabel-diff-header-warnings--diverged: This page was modified by the $1 community. Do not override it unless:
dibabel-diff-header-warnings--diverged-1: Local, changes were done by mistake and should be reverted
dibabel-diff-header-warnings--diverged-2: The, local changes are now included in the primary page
dibabel-diff-header-warnings--diverged-3: The, local changes are no longer needed
dibabel-diff-header-warnings--multisite: This page depends on templates or modules that have not been tagged as "multi-site" in Wikidata. Most of the time this means that page $1 is not yet ready for synchronization, and should not have a multi-site type in $2. Alternatively it could also mean that the page was edited to use a new template/module, and that the new page is not enabled for synchronization.
dibabel-diff-header-warnings--multisite-: Dependencies are not enabled for synchronization
dibabel-diff-summary--localized: Localizing $1 to use this wiki's template and module names. ([[mw:Special:MyLanguage/WP:TNT|docs]])
dibabel-diff-summary--reset: Reseting page to the current content of $1. ([[mw:Special:MyLanguage/WP:TNT|docs]])
dibabel-header-beta--title: Work in progress. Please verify your changes.
dibabel-header-description: Keep modules and templates the same across languages. Written by $1
dibabel-sync-button--title: Multi-page sync is not yet implemented
dibabel-table-externallink--aria: Open external link in a new tab
dibabel-table-icons-protection--title: Indicate if the page has protection and requires special edit rights.
dibabel-table-td-diverged--title: {{PLURAL:$1|One page has|$1 pages have}} local modifications and must be synchronized individually.
dibabel-table-td-hash--title: This hash number represents a unique fingerprint of the current page content. Pages with identical hash have the same content. The hash is computed before page was localized for this wiki. Full hash is $1
dibabel-table-td-outdated--title: {{PLURAL:$1|One page is|$1 pages are}} behind the primary and can be synchronized automatically.
dibabel-table-td-primary--title: Show primary $1 in a new tab.
dibabel-table-td-status--diverged-title: The target page has been modified and cannot be updated automatically.
dibabel-table-td-status--ok-title: The target page is up to date with the primary
dibabel-table-td-status--outdated-link: Show what changed in the last {{PLURAL:$1|1 edit|$1 edits}} of the primary $2 in a new tab.
dibabel-table-td-status--outdated-title: The target page is behind by {{PLURAL:$1|1 edit|$1 edits}}, and can be updated.  Click to see changes.
dibabel-table-td-status--unlocalized-tit: The target page has exactly the same content as original instead of using localized values, and needs to be updated.
dibabel-table-td-unlocalized--title: {{PLURAL:$1|one page is|$1 pages are}} identical to the original. These pages need to be localized because some dependent templates may have different names on that wiki. This can be done automatically.
dibabel-table-td-updated--title: {{PLURAL:$1|One page is|$1 pages are}} up to date.
dibabel-table-th-diverged--title: Number of pages with local modifications.
dibabel-table-th-hash--title: The hash number is a unique fingerprint of the page content. Pages with identical hash have the same content. The hash is computed before page was localized for this wiki.
dibabel-table-th-outdated--title: Number of pages that has fallen behind with the primary.
dibabel-table-th-primary--title: Title of the page at mediawiki.org
dibabel-table-th-status--title: Show if the copied page is in sync with the original, has fallen behind, or has been modified locally (diverged).
dibabel-table-th-unlocalized--title: Number of pages that are identical to the original. These pages need to be localized (e.g. rename dependent templates)
dibabel-table-th-updated--title: Number of up to date pages.
dibabel-table-th-wikipage--title: Title of the copied page as it appears on the destination wiki.
dibabel-updatepage-confirm--description-: Are you sure you want to do this?
